headline: 2 killed, 3 injured when freight train derails in small West Texas city after collision
summary: PECOS, Texas — Two Union Pacific employees were killed and three people were injured when a freight train collided with a tractor-trailer and derailed in a small West Texas city, authorities said...

headline: Union Pacific Corporation Announces Fourth Quarter 2024 Earnings Release Date
summary: OMAHA, Neb., December 19, 2024--Union Pacific Corporation (NYSE: UNP) will release fourth quarter 2024 financial and operating results on Thursday, Jan. 23, 2025, at 7:45 a.m. ET. The company’s management team will host a conference call and live webcast at 8:45 a.m. ET.
